text: Steg-Hohtenn is a municipality in the district of Raron in the canton of Valais in Switzerland. ==History== On 1 January 2009, the former municipalities of Hohtenn and Steg merged into the new municipality of Steg- Hohtenn. ==Villages== * Steg * Hohtenn ==References== ==Other websites== * Official website Category:2009 establishments in Switzerland Category:Municipalities in Raron
